articles.title: [Watch] David Warner Scoops Holder For A Blazing Start In Landmark T20I Vs WI - OneCricket
articles.description: Australian opening batsman David Warner crashes West Indies paceman Jason Holder with a thumping boundary over short fine in the first T20I of their three-match series.
